## Computer Science Discoveries is:



* #### An introductory computer science course for 6 - 10th grade students. 
* #### Mapped to CTSA standards. 
* #### Focused on topics such as problem solving, programming, physical computing, user centered design, and data.
* #### Designed to offer students opportunities to build their own websites, apps, animations, games, physical computing systems and data models.

<div style="clear:both"/>


